com.github.ltennstedt.finnmath.linear

Class AbstractMatrix<E,V,M,N,B>

  • Object
    • AbstractMatrix<E,V,M,N,B>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - The type of the elements of the matrix
    V - The type of the related vector
    M - The type of the matrix
    N - The type of the maximum absolute column sum norm, maximum absolute row sum norm and the maximum norm
    B - The type of the square of the norms
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BigIntMatrix, DecimalMatrix, RealComplexNumberMatrix, SimpleComplexNumberMatrix

    @Beta

extends Object
